-> start node
load configuration / generate UUID
start discovery
    if discover an already known cell, make it active
    else add it to resources known as denied
start ping every cell to see if is active
    if is active, make it active on db
    else make it deactive on db
on peer connection, verify
    if is not at known cells table, add it as denied
        add a entry saying that a miss connection happened (not permited)
    else just connect




